<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>OTP for Password Reset</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
      background-color: #f1f3f5;
      padding: 20px;
      color: #343a40;
    }

    .container {
      background-color: #ffffff;
      padding: 30px 40px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      border: 1px solid #dee2e6;
      max-width: 500px;
      margin: 30px auto;
      box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
      text-align: center;
    }

    h2 {
      color: #0d6efd;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    p {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .otp-box {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 15px 25px;
      font-size: 24px;
      letter-spacing: 6px;
      font-weight: bold;
      background-color: #e9ecef;
      border-radius: 10px;
      color: #212529;
      border: 1px dashed #6c757d;
    }

    .footer {
      margin-top: 30px;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #6c757d;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Password Reset OTP</h2>
    <p>Hello <strong><%= name %></strong>,</p>
    <p>Use the OTP below to reset your password for your <strong>DealSpot</strong> account. This OTP is valid for the next 10 minutes.</p>
    
    <div class="otp-box"><%= otp %></div>

    <p style="margin-top: 25px;">If you didn’t request a password reset, you can safely ignore this email.</p>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>– The DealSpot Team</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
